<https://w3id.org/tklont/explainsInformation> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                              rdfs:subPropertyOf owl:topObjectProperty ;
                                              owl:inverseOf <https://w3id.org/tklont/isExplainedByGroup> ;
                                              rdfs:domain <https://w3id.org/tklont/Indigenous_Local_Community> ;
                                              rdfs:range <https://w3id.org/tklont/Specific_Explanation> .


###  https://w3id.org/tklont/hasAssociationWith
<https://w3id.org/tklont/hasAssociationWith> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                             rdfs:subPropertyOf owl:topObjectProperty ;
                                             rdfs:domain <https://w3id.org/tklont/Material> ;
                                             rdfs:range <https://w3id.org/tklont/Information> ;
                                             rdfs:comment "Material has an association that it wants to display." .


